  "religion": "Rivera is a devout Christian.",
  "politicalViews": "Rivera is a liberal Democrat.",
  "author": "Tom Kershaw",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0729369/bio",
      "sourceTitle": "Naya Rivera – Biography",
      "text": "Rivera is a devout Christian–though there is no indication as to what denomination exactly. But she's obviously serious enough about it to tattoo a large cross on her back."
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "She has mentioned the difficulties associated with fame and religious devotion:"
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.starpulse.com/news/index.php/2012/04/06/sexy_glee_star_naya_rivera_prefers_tv_",
      "sourceTitle": "Sexy 'Glee' Star Naya Rivera Prefers TV High School To The Real Thing: 'I Was Super Flat-Chested and Really Skinny.'",
      "text": "It's hard and sort of sad that you do feel like you need to tread lightly when you say, 'Yes, I do go to church and I read the Bible,' because once you do that people will be like, 'Why are her boobs out? Why is her midriff showing? Why is she playing a lesbian?' I don't want to deal with that stuff, and so I've never really discussed it. It's very personal."
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://global.christianpost.com/news/naya-rivera-pole-dancing-video-stirs-controversy-75276/",
      "sourceTitle": "Naya Rivera Pole Dancing Video Stirs Controversy.",
      "text": "Well, this isn't a surprising revelation considering that, for example, videos have been released of Rivera pole dancing"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "and she occasionally tweets mildly irreverent things like:"
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "sourceUrl": "https://twitter.com/NayaRivera/status/4935349446",
      "sourceTitle": "NayaRivers: Jesus Christ better be playing…",
      "text": "Jesus Christ better be playing at the Hollywood bowl for all this highland traffic to be legit."
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "Given her religiosity, one would imagine that if Jesus were to play the Hollywood bowl, Rivera would know about it."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "text": "Two-pronged politics"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "Rivera's politics have two main themes: 2012 presidential politics and homosexuality."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "She plays a lesbian on the hit show, , and as such, has become a bit of an icon in the gay community. She said:"
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.latina.com/entertainment/buzz/naya-rivera-latina-magazine-cover-may-2012",
      "sourceTitle": "Naya Riveral Latina Magazine Cover: May 2012 Issue, Glee Star Naya Rivera",
      "text": "I get so many tweets a day from people thanking me and saying how the role has changed their lives, enabling them to come out."
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20581651,00.html",
      "sourceTitle": "GLAAD Awards Kiss-Off",
      "text": "She's returned the gratitude in kind, co-hosting the Gay & Lesbian Alliance Against Defamation Awards (GLAAD Awards) and even auctioning off a $5,000 kiss for the organization."
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0729369/bio",
      "sourceTitle": "Naya Rivera – Biography",
      "text": "Plus, she says she frequents gay bars–just a little side-note there."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "In 2012, when the Republicans were battling for the presidential nomination, Rivera expressed extreme dissatisfaction with candidate Rick Santorum. She tweeted:"
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.sheknows.com/entertainment/articles/950015/glee-cast-gets-political-with-rick-santorum-tweets",
      "sourceTitle": "Glee cast gets political with Rick Santorum tweets",
      "text": "And now a political tweet: Rick Santorum is the most disgusting person I've ever seen in my life. Who is this clown?!"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "And:"
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "quote",
      "sourceUrl": "http://www.sheknows.com/entertainment/articles/950015/glee-cast-gets-political-with-rick-santorum-tweets",
      "sourceTitle": "Glee cast gets political with Rick Santorum tweets",
      "text": "And why are Americans letting [Santorum] open his ignorant mouth? #embarrassing"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "When Obama ultimately won the election, she celebrated at a post-election party, and in the , she looks pretty happy."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    },
    {
      "type": "sentence",
      "text": "So, liberal Democrat seems an appropriate title."
    },
    {
      "type": "break"
    }
  ],
